<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>한끼줍쇼</title>
    <!-- CSS 참조 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="public/main.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Jua&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Do+Hyeon&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- tailwindcss 참조 -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Jua', sans-serif;
        }
        
        h1, h2 {
            font-family: 'Do Hyeon', sans-serif;
        }

        .stroke h1, .stroke h7 {
            text-shadow:
                2px 2px 0 #000,
                -2px -2px 0 #000,
                -2px 2px 0 #000,
                2px -2px 0 #000,
                2px 0 0 #000,
                -2px 0 0 #000,
                0 2px 0 #000,
                0 -2px 0 #000;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            background-color: rgba(247, 159, 129, 0.3);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1rem;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .testimonial-card {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .testimonial-card blockquote {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        .testimonial-card .author {
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
        }

        .testimonial-card .author-title {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #999;
        }
        .button-info:hover {
            background-color: #f5f5f5cc;
        }
        .button-info {
            background-color: white;
            color: #F79F81;
            padding: 10px;
            padding-left: 17px;
            padding-right: 17px;
            /* border: 1px solid black; */
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease; /* 트랜지션 추가 */
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
        <header class="px-4 lg:px-6 h-14 flex items-center bg-[#F79F81] text-white" style="text-shadow: -1px 0px 1px black, 0px 1px 1px black, 1px 1px 1px black, 0px -1px 1px black;">
            <a class="flex items-center justify-center" href="/">
                <span style="font-size: 22px;">한끼줍쇼</span>
            </a>
            <nav class="ml-auto flex gap-4 sm:gap-6">
                <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/menu">학식 메뉴</a>
                <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/list">학식 이야기</a>
                <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/subscribe">구독하기</a>
                <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/info">식당 정보</a>
                <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/FAQ">자주 묻는 질문</a>
                <!-- <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/login">로그인</a>
                <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/logout">로그아웃</a> -->
                <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/register">회원가입</a>
                <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
                    <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/login">로그인</a>
                <% } %>
                <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-gray-200 no-underline" href="/mypage">마이페이지</a>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <main class="flex-1">
            <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 xl:py-48 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#F79F81] to-[#F5BCA9] text-white">
                <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-4 text-center">
                        <div class="space-y-2">
                            <div class="stroke">
                                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white">
                                    한끼줍쇼    
                                </h1>
                            </div>
                            <p class="mx-auto max-w-[700px] text-gray-100 md:text-xl">
                                한끼줍쇼를 구독하고 이메일로 오늘의 메뉴를 받아보세요 :)
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-x-4">
                            <a class="button-info"
                                href="/subscribe">구독하기</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
                <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
                    <div class="grid items-center gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_500px] lg:gap-12 xl:grid-cols-[1fr_550px]">
                        <img
                        style="border: 0.5px solid black;"
                            class="mx-auto aspect-video overflow-hidden rounded-xl object-fit object-center sm:w-full lg:order-last"
                            height="310" src="public/image/구독하기페이지.png" width="550" />
                        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-4">
                            <div class="highlight text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">구독</div>
                            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">구독 기능</h2>
                            <p class="max-w-[600px] text-gray-600 md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed dark:text-gray-400" style="padding-bottom: 107px;">
                                구독을 하시면 오늘의 식당별 점심 메뉴를 학교 어플을 확인하지 않고 매일 오전 10시에 이메일로 편하게 받아보실 수 있어요.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
                <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
                    <div class="grid items-center gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[500px_1fr] lg:gap-12 xl:grid-cols-[550px_1fr]">
                        <img
                        style="border: 0.5px solid black;"
                        class="mx-auto aspect-video overflow-hidden rounded-xl object-fit object-center sm:w-full"
                        height="310" src="public/image/학식이야기.png" width="550" />
                        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-4">
                            <div class="highlight text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">학식 이야기</div>
                            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">학식 이야기 기능</h2>
                            <p class="max-w-[600px] text-gray-600 md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed dark:text-gray-400" style="padding-bottom: 107px;">
                                오늘의 학식에 대해 평가하는 글을 작성할 수 있어요. 이 평가들을 토대로 오늘 더 맛있는 메뉴의 식당을 선택해서 먹을 수 있어요.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
                <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
                    <div class="grid items-center gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_500px] lg:gap-12 xl:grid-cols-[1fr_550px]">
                        <img style="border: 0.5px solid black;" class="mx-auto aspect-video overflow-hidden rounded-xl object-fit object-center sm:w-full lg:order-last"
                            height="310" src="public/image/구글맵.png" width="550" />
                        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-4">
                            <div class="highlight text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">식당 정보</div>
                            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">식당 정보 안내</h2>
                            <p class="max-w-[600px] text-gray-600 md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed dark:text-gray-400" style="padding-bottom: 75px;">
                                식당 정보 페이지를 들어가면 후생관 학생 식당, 교직원 식당, 기숙사 식당의 위치와 운영 시간 등을 파악하실 수 있어요. 
                                대략적인 위치 파악을 위해 구글맵에 표시해두었어요.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#F79F81] to-[#F5BCA9] text-white">
                <div class="container grid items-center justify-center gap-4 px-4 text-center md:px-6 lg:gap-10">
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <div class="stroke">
                            <h7 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white">사용자 후기</h7>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mx-auto max-w-[700px] text-gray-100 md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed">
                            한끼줍쇼를 이용한 사용자들의 후기를 확인해보세요
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid w-full grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
                        <div class="testimonial-card">
                            <blockquote class="text-lg font-semibold leading-snug">"한끼줍쇼 덕분에 매일매일의 식당별 점심 메뉴를 직접 어플로 확인하지 않고 편하게 이메일로 받을 수 있어서 좋았어요."</blockquote>
                            <div class="author">임건우</div>
                            <div class="author-title">대학생</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-card">
                            <blockquote class="text-lg font-semibold leading-snug">"한끼줍쇼 덕분에 매일매일 게시글을 통해 더 나은 메뉴를 선택해서 먹을 수 있어서 좋았어요."</blockquote>
                            <div class="author">이소은</div>
                            <div class="author-title">대학생</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-card">
                            <blockquote class="text-lg font-semibold leading-snug">"한끼줍쇼 덕분에 식당의 위치를 쉽게 알 수 있었고 하나의 학식 커뮤니티가 만들어진 것 같아 좋았어요."</blockquote>
                            <div class="author">이재인</div>
                            <div class="author-title">대학생</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <footer class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row py-6 w-full shrink-0 items-center px-4 md:px-6 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">© 2024 한끼줍쇼. All rights reserved.</p>
            <nav class="sm:ml-auto flex gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            </nav>
        </footer>
        
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.9.1/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.9.1/TimelineLite.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.9.1/EasePack.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-0pUGZvbkm6XF6gxjEnlmuGrJXVbNuzT9qBBavbLwCsOGabYfZo0T0to5eqruptLy" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="public/style.js"></script>
</body>

</html>